<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>전체 시스템 아키텍처 - Zero Trust Infra</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #070d14;
    --panel: #0b1520;
    --border: #1a3a5c;
    --accent-blue: #00d4ff;
    --accent-green: #00ff88;
    --accent-red: #ff3355;
    --accent-yellow: #ffcc00;
    --accent-orange: #ff8c00;
    --text: #c8e6ff;
    --dim: #4a7a9b;
    --glow-blue: 0 0 12px #00d4ff66;
    --glow-green: 0 0 12px #00ff8866;
    --glow-red: 0 0 12px #ff335566;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Grid bg */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .page {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 30px 40px 50px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  header p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* Zone containers */
  .diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .zone {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--panel);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .zone-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 20px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* External zone */
  .zone-external {
    border-color: #553344;
    background: #0d0810;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .zone-external .zone-label {
    background: #553344;
    color: var(--accent-red);
  }

  /* VPN zone */
  .zone-vpn {
    border-color: #1a4a7a;
    background: #080f18;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .zone-vpn .zone-label {
    background: #1a4a7a;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
  }

  /* Internal zone */
  .zone-internal {
    border-color: #1a4a3a;
    background: #060e0a;
  }
  .zone-internal .zone-label {
    background: #1a4a3a;
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }

  /* Node grid */
  .nodes {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  /* Node box */
  .node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .node-box {
    border: 1px solid;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    min-width: 120px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .node-box:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .node-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .node-name {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .node-desc {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Node color variants */
  .node-red .node-box {
    border-color: var(--accent-red);
    background: #1a050a;
    box-shadow: var(--glow-red);
  }
  .node-red .node-name { color: var(--accent-red); }

  .node-blue .node-box {
    border-color: var(--accent-blue);
    background: #040e18;
    box-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
  }
  .node-blue .node-name { color: var(--accent-blue); }

  .node-yellow .node-box {
    border-color: var(--accent-yellow);
    background: #141006;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px #ffcc0044;
  }
  .node-yellow .node-name { color: var(--accent-yellow); }

  .node-green .node-box {
    border-color: var(--accent-green);
    background: #04100a;
    box-shadow: var(--glow-green);
  }
  .node-green .node-name { color: var(--accent-green); }

  .node-orange .node-box {
    border-color: var(--accent-orange);
    background: #120a04;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px #ff8c0044;
  }
  .node-orange .node-name { color: var(--accent-orange); }

  /* VIP badge */
  .vip-badge {
    background: #0a1f3a;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
    box-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* Connectors between zones */
  .connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 4px 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .arrow-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6px 0;
  }

  .arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .arrow-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 28px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .arrow-line::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    border-left: 5px solid transparent;
    border-right: 5px solid transparent;
  }

  .arrow-blocked .arrow-line {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-red), #ff335588);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px #ff335566;
  }
  .arrow-blocked .arrow-line::after {
    border-top: 7px solid var(--accent-red);
  }
  .arrow-blocked .arrow-label { color: var(--accent-red); }

  .arrow-allowed .arrow-line {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-green), #00ff8888);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px #00ff8866;
  }
  .arrow-allowed .arrow-line::after {
    border-top: 7px solid var(--accent-green);
  }
  .arrow-allowed .arrow-label { color: var(--accent-green); }

  .arrow-label {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 90px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .block-icon {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-red);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-red);
  }

  /* Sub-zones inside internal */
  .sub-zones {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sub-zone {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
    border: 1px dashed;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sub-zone-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 14px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .sub-zone-app {
    border-color: #2255aa;
  }
  .sub-zone-app .sub-zone-label {
    background: #0b1a30;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .sub-zone-db {
    border-color: #225533;
  }
  .sub-zone-db .sub-zone-label {
    background: #0a1a10;
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }

  /* Feature tags */
  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin: 2px 2px 0;
    border: 1px solid;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .tag-blue { border-color: #1a5588; color: #5599cc; background: #040e1a; }
  .tag-green { border-color: #1a5533; color: #44aa77; background: #04100a; }
  .tag-red { border-color: #552233; color: #cc4466; background: #10040a; }
  .tag-yellow { border-color: #554422; color: #ccaa33; background: #100e04; }

  /* Internal arrow */
  .int-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    padding: 3px 0;
    text-shadow: var(--glow-green);
  }

  .int-arrow-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-green), #00ff8844);
    box-shadow: 0 0 4px #00ff8844;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Legend */
  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid;
  }

  /* Status pulse */
  .pulse {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-green);
    box-shadow: var(--glow-green);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.8); }
  }

  .status-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .status-ok { color: var(--accent-green); }

  /* Animation */
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .zone { animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease both; }
  .zone:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .zone:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .zone:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  /* VPN cluster inner layout */
  .vpn-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .vip-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .vip-box {
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-blue);
    background: #050e1a;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: var(--glow-blue), inset 0 0 20px #00d4ff11;
    animation: pulse-ring 3s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-ring {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 12px #00d4ff66, inset 0 0 20px #00d4ff11; }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 24px #00d4ffaa, inset 0 0 30px #00d4ff22; }
  }

  .vip-ip {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    text-shadow: var(--glow-blue);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ha-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    color: var(--accent-yellow);
  }

  .ha-line {
    height: 2px;
    width: 50px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-yellow) 0px, var(--accent-yellow) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 10px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px #ffcc0044;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <header>
    <h1>🛡️ ZERO-TRUST INFRASTRUCTURE</h1>
    <p>서버 및 DB 접근 제어 아키텍처 · 최종 산출물</p>
  </header>

  <div class="status-bar">
    <span><span class="pulse"></span><span class="status-ok">HA ACTIVE</span></span>
    <span>VPN <span class="status-ok">ONLINE</span></span>
    <span>FIREWALL <span class="status-ok">RUNNING</span></span>
  </div>

  <div class="diagram">

    <div class="zone zone-external">
      <span class="zone-label">🌐 외부망 (EXTERNAL NETWORK: 172.20.x.x)</span>
      <div class="nodes">
        <div class="node node-red">
          <div class="node-box">
            <span class="node-icon">💀</span>
            <div class="node-name">attacker</div>
            <div class="node-desc">악의적 외부 접근<br>Nmap / Hydra 공격 시도</div>
          </div>
          <div class="tag tag-red">UNTRUSTED</div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center; color: var(--dim); font-size:0.7rem; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;">
          ──────── vs ────────
        </div>

        <div class="node node-yellow">
          <div class="node-box">
            <span class="node-icon">👤</span>
            <div class="node-name">client</div>
            <div class="node-desc">인가된 개발자 기기<br>VPN 자동 라우팅 설정 완료</div>
          </div>
          <div class="tag tag-yellow">AUTHORIZED</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="connector">
      <div class="arrow-group">
        <div class="arrow arrow-blocked">
          <div class="arrow-label">포트 직접 타격<br>(Drop / Timeout)</div>
          <div class="arrow-line"></div>
          <div class="block-icon">🚫</div>
          <div class="arrow-label">BLOCKED</div>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow arrow-allowed">
          <div class="arrow-label">인가된 접속<br>(IP Route via VIP)</div>
          <div class="arrow-line"></div>
          <div class="arrow-label" style="color:var(--accent-green)">✅ ALLOWED</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="zone zone-vpn">
      <span class="zone-label">🔐 HA VPN CLUSTER (Keepalived VRRP)</span>
      <div class="vpn-inner">

        <div class="node node-blue">
          <div class="node-box">
            <span class="node-icon">🖥️</span>
            <div class="node-name">vpn-active</div>
            <div class="node-desc">Master Gateway<br>eth1: 192.168.50.101</div>
          </div>
          <div class="tag tag-blue">PRIMARY</div>
        </div>

        <div class="ha-link">
          <div class="ha-line"></div>
          <span style="color:var(--accent-yellow); font-size:0.8rem;">⚡</span>
          <div class="ha-line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="vip-node">
          <div class="vip-box">
            <span style="font-size:1.3rem;">🌐</span>
            <div class="vip-ip">VIP<br>172.20.0.100</div>
          </div>
          <div class="vip-badge">VIRTUAL IP (HA)</div>
        </div>

        <div class="ha-link">
          <div class="ha-line"></div>
          <span style="color:var(--accent-yellow); font-size:0.8rem;">⚡</span>
          <div class="ha-line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="node node-blue">
          <div class="node-box">
            <span class="node-icon">💻</span>
            <div class="node-name">vpn-standby</div>
            <div class="node-desc">Backup Gateway<br>eth2: 172.20.0.102</div>
          </div>
          <div class="tag tag-yellow">FAILOVER READY</div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:10px; font-size:0.62rem; color:var(--dim); font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;">
        ⚡ SPOF 완벽 제거 · Active 다운 시 Standby가 VIP 즉시 인계 (Ping 무중단)
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="connector">
      <div class="arrow-group">
        <div class="arrow arrow-allowed">
          <div class="arrow-label">VPN 터널<br>내부망 연결</div>
          <div class="arrow-line"></div>
          <div class="arrow-label" style="color:var(--accent-green)">🔒 TUNNEL</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="zone zone-internal">
      <span class="zone-label">🏗️ 마이크로 세그멘테이션 내부망 (INTERNAL: 192.168.50.x)</span>

      <div class="sub-zones">

        <div class="sub-zone sub-zone-app">
          <span class="sub-zone-label">📦 APP 구역</span>
          <div class="node node-blue" style="padding-top:10px;">
            <div class="node-box" style="min-width:180px;">
              <span class="node-icon">🌐</span>
              <div class="node-name">app-server</div>
              <div class="node-desc">192.168.50.10<br>Python 이상 탐지 데몬 백그라운드 가동</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:3px; justify-content:center; margin-top:4px;">
              <div class="tag tag-blue">SSH KEY-ONLY</div>
              <div class="tag tag-green">WEBHOOK ALERTS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:10px; padding:8px; background:#040e18; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #1a3a5c;">
            <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.6rem; color:var(--dim);">
              🐍 Python Anomaly Detector
            </div>
            <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.58rem; color: #4488aa; margin-top:3px; line-height:1.5;">
              → /var/log/auth.log 실시간 Generator 감시<br>
              → Logrotate (Inode 변경) 자동 재오픈 감지<br>
              → Node.js 서버로 Webhook 경고 실시간 발송<br>
              → Password 인증 완전 차단 (Permission Denied)
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:6px; min-width:60px;">
          <div style="font-size:0.6rem; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; color:var(--accent-green); text-align:center; text-shadow:var(--glow-green);">
            DB 쿼리<br>접근
          </div>
          <div style="width:2px; height:40px; background:linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-green), #00ff8844); box-shadow:0 0 6px #00ff8844;"></div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;">→</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sub-zone sub-zone-db">
          <span class="sub-zone-label">🗄️ DB 구역</span>
          <div class="node node-green" style="padding-top:10px;">
            <div class="node-box" style="min-width:180px;">
              <span class="node-icon">🗄️</span>
              <div class="node-name">db-server</div>
              <div class="node-desc">192.168.50.20<br>MariaDB 심층 은닉</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:3px; justify-content:center; margin-top:4px;">
              <div class="tag tag-green">LEAST PRIVILEGE</div>
              <div class="tag tag-red">PORT 3306 ISOLATED</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:10px; padding:8px; background:#04100a; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #1a4a3a;">
            <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.6rem; color:var(--dim);">
              🔒 DB 접근 제어 및 탈취 방어
            </div>
            <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.58rem; color: #449966; margin-top:3px; line-height:1.5;">
              → 3306 포트 외부망 접근 완전 차단 (Timeout)<br>
              → DB 내부 app_user 계정에 최소 권한 부여<br>
              → 앱 계정 탈취 후 DROP TABLE 시도 방어<br>
              → (ERROR 1142: DROP command denied)
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:14px; padding:10px 16px; background:#100508; border:1px solid #552233; border-radius:6px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;">
        <span style="font-size:1.2rem;">🛡️</span>
        <div style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.62rem; color: var(--accent-red); text-shadow: var(--glow-red);">
          Zero-Trust 인증 통제 : 내부망 감염 기기(Client)의 SSH 무차별 대입 공격조차 패스워드 통제 정책에 의해 완벽히 방어됨
        </div>
        <span style="margin-left:auto; color:var(--accent-red); font-size:0.7rem; font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;">DEFENDED ✓</span>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div><div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-item">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="border-color:var(--accent-red); background:#1a050a;"></div>
      비인가 해커 공격 경로 (차단됨)
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="border-color:var(--accent-green); background:#04100a;"></div>
      인가된 VPN 터널 / 내부 통신 (허용됨)
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <div class="legend-dot" style="border-color:var(--accent-yellow); background:#141006;"></div>
      Keepalived VRRP 헬스체크 연결
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>